The yazd-thesis class
-----------------------

This class file has been written for the Yazd university students to
easily write their theses and dissertations.

Author: Vahid Damanafshan <vdamanafshan@gmail.com>
Copyright (C) 2015-2019 by Vahid Damanafshan 
http://xelinic.ir
vdamanafshan@gmail.com



To run the root file, you must have B Nazanin, Yas, and
Times New Roman fonts on your computer and run XeLaTeX on the file.


